  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nWhen `WARN Error connecting to eth1 node endpoint  action: trying fallbacks` appears in the output, there is no INFO output explicitly stating that connection to the fallback node succeeded.  I think this would be reassuring, as I ended up running a tcpdump on my fallback node just to verify that traffic was hitting it.\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nlighthouse v1.4.0-3b600ac (stable)\r\nrustc 1.53.0 (53cb7b09b 2021-06-17)\r\n",
